  "detailed_description": "Descend into the Backrooms as a newly hired researcher to locate previous teams who went missing during their expedition. However, after arriving at your first destination you soon realize why this seemingly endless labyrinth of rooms and endless buzzing may make you the next researcher lost in the Backrooms. Will you survive and find the main research team before it's too late?<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Co-op</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2728250/extras/1ddc28d9c1e80d1b01759339948bf18c.poster.avif?t=1715490934\" width=616 height=266 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2728250/extras/1ddc28d9c1e80d1b01759339948bf18c.webm?t=1715490934\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2728250/extras/1ddc28d9c1e80d1b01759339948bf18c.mp4?t=1715490934\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>You can host or join your friends to experience this game together. Proximity voice chat can be used in game for a more immersive experience.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Entities</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2728250/extras/d777da21804b7fd576ebd9f6944e2970.poster.avif?t=1715490934\" width=616 height=266 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2728250/extras/d777da21804b7fd576ebd9f6944e2970.webm?t=1715490934\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2728250/extras/d777da21804b7fd576ebd9f6944e2970.mp4?t=1715490934\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Explore and find the potentially hostile entities inside the Backrooms.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Immersive Levels</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn